## Hardware[¶](#hardware "Permalink to this headline")

The Dawn (PVC) nodes are:

* 256 Dell PowerEdge XE9640 servers

each consisting of:

* 2x Intel(R) Xeon(R) Platinum 8468 (formerly codenamed Sapphire Rapids) (96 cores in total)
* 1024 GiB RAM
* 4x Intel(R) Data Center GPU Max 1550 GPUs (formerly codenamed Ponte Vecchio) (128 GiB GPU RAM each)
* Xe-Link 4-way GPU interconnect within the node
* Quad-rail NVIDIA (Mellanox) HDR200 InfiniBand interconnect

and each PVC GPU contains two stacks (previously known as tiles) and 1024 compute units.'}, {'rank': 7, 'doc_id': 'https://slurm.schedmd.com/rest_api.html::chunk::0134', 'score': 0.8833179723502298, 'source': 'external_docs', 'retrieval_sources': ['external_docs'], 'retrieval_source_ranks': {'external_docs': 2}, 'retrieval_signal_trace': {'dense_rank': 2, 'dense_score': 0.51690423, 'signal_type': 'dense'}, 'source_authority': 'external_official', 'authority_tier': 2, 'validity_status': 'unknown', 'freshness_hint': None, 'title': None, 'doc_title': None, 'system_names': [], 'partition_names': [], 'service_names': [], 'scope_family_names': [], 'software_names': [], 'software_versions': [], 'module_names': [], 'toolchain_names': [], 'toolchain_versions': [], 'official_doc_matches': [], 'rerank_trace': {'authority_feature': 0.5, 'base_rank': 6, 'base_rrf_score': 0.016129032258064516, 'final_score': 0.8833179723502298, 'freshness_feature': 0.0, 'query_constraints': {'module_names': [], 'partition_names': [], 'query_type': 'local_operational', 'scope_family_names': ['pvc'], 'scope_required': True, 'service_names': [], 'software_names': [], 'software_versions': [], 'system_names': ['Dawn - Intel GPU (PVC) Nodes'], 'toolchain_names': [], 'toolchain_versions': [], 'version_sensitive_guess': None}, 'reranker_type': 'validity_aware', 'scope_family_effective_feature': 0.0, 'scope_family_feature': 0.0, 'scope_family_gate_reason': 'applied', 'scope_feature': 0.0, 'semantic_base': 0.8433179723502298, 'software_feature': 0.0, 'source_ranks': {'external_docs': 2}, 'status_feature': 0.0, 'version_feature': 0.0, 'weighted_contributions': {'authority_feature': 0.04, 'freshness_feature': 0.0, 'scope_family_feature': 0.0, 'scope_feature': 0.0, 'software_feature': 0.0, 'status_feature': 0.0, 'version_feature': 0.0}}, 'text': "rt (UNIX timestamp) (UNIX timestamp or time string recognized by Slurm (e.g., '[MM/DD[/YY]-]HH:MM[:SS]')) format: int64

